---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Knowledge
description: "Briefs, field notes, and shared thinking emerging from The Future Herd."
hero_image: "/assets/img/knowledge-hero.png"
hero_alt: "A visual representation of shared knowledge and interconnected systems"
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-image">
    <img
      src="{{ heroImage }}"
      alt="{{ heroAlt }}"
      loading="eager"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="tagline">{{ description }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<p>
This is a growing commons of leadership briefs and shared thinking emerging from conversations on <em>The Future Herd</em>.
These artifacts are designed to stand on their own, while remaining connected to the dialogues that shaped them.
</p>

<ul class="knowledge-list">
{% for item in collections.knowledge | reverse %}
  <li class="latest-card">
    {% if item.data.image %}
      <a class="latest-thumb" href="{{ item.url }}">
        <img
          src="{{ item.data.image }}"
          alt="{{ item.data.imageAlt or item.data.title }}"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </a>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="latest-body">
      <a class="latest-title" href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>

      {% if item.data.subtitle %}
        <p class="tagline">{{ item.data.subtitle }}</p>
      {% elseif item.data.abstract %}
        <p class="tagline">{{ item.data.abstract }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
